{"tid":1391563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後喺街比藍屍打點處理？","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:16:34.000Z","uid":252960,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"566b71fcaeda05d703c0de2efa7e15627cb5cd3d","tid":1391563,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"還拖，有人報警 --&gt; 一齊被拉，但只會charge你<br />\n唔還，有人報警 --&gt; 被黑警氹你返警署，charge你涉嫌襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我認為既正確處理步驟：唔還拖但會儘量避，同時大聲嗌召喚手足圍觀；自己唔好報警，警察黎咗就一齊指證對方打人，問題係警察要求你返差館協助調查（參考天水圍兩個學生被人打既案例，黑警會氹你話返到差館先做到野），呢一步要點拆呢？跟佢返去會被屈襲擊罪，唔跟又會被佢屈不合作，暫時諗到最理想情況係周圍手足一齊起哄，唔比黑警的你返去，但佢可能就話「你唔返去我就唔拉人」最後眼白白睇住藍屍施施然走人。"},{"pid":"09eca1f153a309197e3c523251b467a7c6f28b21","tid":1391563,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"[突發] 獨立調查委員會報告出咗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtJuuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtJuuS</a>"},{"pid":"31d38fe5a0d93d7bddf889627a882dc64704ee79","tid":1391563,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74fd2064554ac3981cc785b03fb399f2783a4533","tid":1391563,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbf3574fd6ccb13d0bb54775cf761fd21eb01152","tid":1391563,"uid":220864,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:28.000Z","msg":"第一步 還拖<br />\n第二步 走<br />\n和理非上前"},{"pid":"fb8d8464bfa7d97dc2936aa5ffd471a2d0d5afd1","tid":1391563,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"如果唔夠打點算? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbe922886fd70bc2c39cdc0067599134116fbba","tid":1391563,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"傘陣 散場"},{"pid":"27ee85916274913f210de4d3207cf65b61880fb5","tid":1391563,"uid":145235,"like":5,"